<h2>JavaScript(CHR)</h2>

<p>JavaScript does not create a new scope for each code block.</p>

<p>This code will display the value of i (10), even OUTSIDE the for loop block:</p>

<p id="demo"></p>

<script>
for (var i = 0; i < 10; i++) {
  // some code
}
document.getElementById("demo").innerHTML = i;
</script>

</body>
</html>
